; Auto-generated placeholder for Lapis Bay.
; Drop real environment art under MeshRoot; lighting/atmosphere already tuned.
; Atmosphere: Storm-grey port chained with rusted hawsers. Drowned sailors crawl up at low tide. Black-sail crews drink in shacks. Salt-witches pay better than the Crown.
; Palette: Slate-blue · pirate-flag black · pale lapis
; Level range: 12-22

